Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.62,Main,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,.أوتسورو
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:20.14,Main,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,.يوشيدا شويو
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:21.81,Main,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,.لا
